《'''-{zh-hk:小丑回魂;zh-tw:牠;zh-cn:小丑回魂;}-'''》（{{lang-en|''I-{}-t''}}，或稱作{{lang|en|''It: Chapter One''}}）是一部2017年[[美國|美國]]{{link-en|靈異題材|Supernatural fiction|超自然}}[[恐怖片|恐怖片]]，由[[安迪·馬希提|安迪·馬希提]]執導，查斯·帕瑪、[[凱瑞·福永|凱瑞·福永]]與[[蓋瑞·道柏曼|蓋瑞·道柏曼]]共同負責撰寫劇本。電影改編自[[史蒂芬·金|史蒂芬·金]]的1986年同名小說《[[牠_(小說)|牠]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thewrap.com/stephen-kings-it-release-date-set-by-warner-bros/|title=Stephen King's 'It' Release Date Set by Warner Bros|last=Geier|first=Thom|work=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]|date=2016-04-22|accessdate=2016-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161024120617/http://www.thewrap.com/stephen-kings-it-release-date-set-by-warner-bros/|archive-date=2016-10-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2016/4/24/11498018/stephen-king-it-release-date|title=Stephen King's It will hit theaters on September 18th, 2017|last=Opam|first=Kwame|work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|date=2016-04-24|accessdate=2016-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018041007/http://www.theverge.com/2016/4/24/11498018/stephen-king-it-release-date|archive-date=2016-10-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。故事描述七名少年遭到「牠」盯上，而陷入各自的恐懼之中；金給予該故事的主題為「記憶、童年創傷，以及隱藏在傳統小鎮價值觀背後的醜陋。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://moviepilot.com/posts/3950075|title=Pennywise Up! Everything We Know About Stephen King's 'It' Remake|last=Opie|first=David|work=[[Moviepilot|Moviepilot]]|date=2015-06-03|accessdate=2016-06-28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161012121741/http://moviepilot.com/posts/3950075|archivedate=2016年10月12日|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/booksblog/2015/oct/06/stephen-king-it-scares-off-film-makers-cary-fukunaga|title=Why Stephen King's IT scares off film-makers|last=Opie|first=David|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=2015-10-06|accessdate=2016-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160609193420/https://www.theguardian.com/books/booksblog/2015/oct/06/stephen-king-it-scares-off-film-makers-cary-fukunaga|archive-date=2016-06-09|dead-ur