==發行==
《牠》被排於2017年9月8日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bloody-disgusting.com/movie/3388740/will-play-pennywise-stephen-kings/|title=Who Will Play Pennywise in Stephen King's 'It'?|last=Disgusting|first=Mr|work=Bloody Disgusting|date=2016-04-25|accessdate=2016-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161023060818/http://bloody-disgusting.com/movie/3388740/will-play-pennywise-stephen-kings/|archive-date=2016-10-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年3月7日，史蒂芬·金宣布電影的標題為《Part 1 – The Losers' Club》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/it-movie-review-stephen-king/#it-movie-stephen-king-review|title=Stephen King Says the New 'It' Movie Succeeds Beyond Expectations|last=Foutch|first=Haleigh|work=Collider.com|date=2017-03-12|accessdate=2017-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312222910/http://collider.com/it-movie-review-stephen-king/#it-movie-stephen-king-review|archive-date=2017-03-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/stephen-king-it-movie-remake-verdict-a7617811.html|title=Stephen King calls It remake a 'wonderful production'|last=Shepherd|first=Jack|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|date=2017-03-12|accessdate=2017-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170314064243/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/stephen-king-it-movie-remake-verdict-a7617811.html|archive-date=2017-03-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===評價===
《牠》獲得了多數正面的評價。在[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]網站上，根據355條評論而得到了85%的新鮮度，平均得分7.24 / 10；該網站共識：「良好的表現、惡魔般的可怕與以情感影響的故事為核心。《牠》放大了史蒂芬·金經典故事中的恐怖，而沒有失去其核心上的觸及。」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/it_2017/|title=It (2017)|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2017-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015132845/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/it_2017/|archive-date=2017-10-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，其得分達69<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/it|title=It reviews|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2017-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170909131055/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/it|archive-date=2017-09-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾在A+至F間的評價落在「B+」<ref name=opening/>。

===票房===
在美國和加拿大，《牠》與《{{le|911絕命電梯|9/11 (2017 film)}}》、《{{le|愛情齡距離|Home Again (2017 film)}}》共同上映和競爭，外界預估《牠》在首週末能獲得5000萬至6000萬美元的票房<ref name="preview" />。在上映前一週，首週末的預估值提高至6000萬至7000萬美元，如果口碑好的話有機會開得更高<ref>{{cite web|url=https://mobile.nytimes.com/2017/09/03/movies/hollywood-summer-box-office-movie-ticket-sales.amp.html|title=After Dismal Summer, Hollywood Pins Hopes on Fall Ticket Sales|author=Brooks Barnes|website=''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]''|date=2017-09-03|accessdate=2017-09-06|archive-date=2018-08-30|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/723zEZWw5?url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/09/03/movies/hollywood-summer-box-office-movie-ticket-sales.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=preview>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/09/it-stephen-king-movie-weekend-box-office-1202161829/|title=Box Office To Wake Up From Long Summer’s Nap As ‘It’ Happens With $60Ms Opening, Possible $70M – Preview|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2017-09-05|access-date=2017-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906223124/http://deadline.com/2017/09/it-stephen-king-movie-weekend-box-office-1202161829/|archive-date=2017-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該片將在4103間戲院放映，成為R級電影的最高戲院數（超越了《[[羅根_(電影)|羅根]]》於3月的4071間）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4322&p=.htm|title=Adaptation of Stephen King's 'It' Targets Fall Opening Weekend Record|website=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|date=2017-09-07|access-date=2017-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910043306/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4322&p=.htm|archive-date=2017-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在上映的前幾天，《牠》打破了[[Fandango_(公司)|Fandango]]的預售記錄（超越了《[[鬼入鏡3|鬼入鏡3]]》（2011年）的紀錄），成為史上最高的恐怖片預售額，同時也在該網站於9月的預售前三名的紀錄（超越了《[[薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟|薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟]]》（2016年）的紀錄）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pro.boxoffice.com/shatters-fandango-presales-records-horror-movies-september-releases/|title=Fandango: ‘IT’ Shatters Presales Records for Horror Movies and September Releases|website=''Box Office Pro''|date=2017-09-06|accessdate=2017-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170907124137/http://pro.boxoffice.com/shatters-fandango-presales-records-horror-movies-september-releases/|archive-date=2017-09-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。《牠》在美國週四晚間的首映獲得了1350萬美元的票房，這打破了R級的恐怖片的紀錄（超越了2016年電影《[[惡棍英雄：死侍|惡棍英雄：死侍]]》（1260萬美元）的紀錄）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2017/09/08/box-office-it-nets-record-crushing-13-5-million-thursday/|title=Box Office: 'It' Scares Up Record-Crushing $13.5 Million Thursday|author=Scott Mendelson|website=''[[Forbes|Forbes]]''|date=2017-09-08|accessdate=2017-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908203353/https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2017/09/08/box-office-it-nets-record-crushing-13-5-million-thursday/|archive-date=2017-09-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於該片在週四的突出表現，使得[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]透露，有些分析家甚至將週末的預估值提高至9000萬美元。《牠》在首映當天票房達5100萬美元（包括週四的票房），使首週末的票房預估值提升至1億美元；儘管該表現勝過《惡棍英雄：死侍》（4730萬美元），但仍輸給《鬼入鏡3》（5260萬美元）<ref name=opening>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/09/stephen-king-it-home-again-box-office-1202163667/|title=Crazed Clown Cashes Smashes Sept., Genre Records As Stephen King’s ‘It’ Pulls In $123M+ Opening|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=2017-09-11|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6tO6J3KIE?url=http://deadline.com/2017/09/stephen-king-it-home-again-box-office-1202163667/|archive-date=2017-09-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該片於美國首週末票房收入達1.172億美元，成為了9月上映的恐怖片中的最高紀錄，同時也是R級電影的第二高首週末成績（僅次於《惡棍英雄：死侍》的1.344億美元）。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》和Deadline都認為，如果不是[[颶風艾瑪|颶風艾瑪]]使[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]]近50%的戲院關閉營業，那《牠》的首週末票房成績應該會更高，而這也佔了美國總票房的5%<ref name=Variety>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2017/film/news/it-box-office-stephen-king-movie-opening-weekend-1202553361/|title=Box Office: Stephen King’s ‘It’ Smashes Records With Massive $117 Million Opening|publisher=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=2017-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910165829/http://variety.com/2017/film/news/it-box-office-stephen-king-movie-opening-weekend-1202553361/|archive-date=2017-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

台灣方面，首週四天票房為新台幣4035萬元<ref>{{cite news |author1=洪文 |title=恐怖小丑《牠》票房曝光！2倍打趴《安娜貝爾2》 |url=https://movies.ettoday.net/news/1008829 |work=[[ETtoday|ETtoday]] |date=2017-09-11 |access-date=2018-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180215143627/https://movies.ettoday.net/news/1008829 |archive-date=2018-02-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；最終全台票房為新台幣1.16億元<ref>{{cite web |title=全國電影票房2018年01/15-01/21統計資訊 |url=https://www.tfi.org.tw/Content/TFI/PublicInfo/全國電影票房2018年0115-0121統計資訊.pdf |website=[[國家電影中心|國家電影中心]] |date=2018-01-25 |access-date=2019-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180628153022/https://www.tfi.org.tw/Content/TFI/PublicInfo/%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E7%A5%A8%E6%88%BF2018%E5%B9%B40115-0121%E7%B5%B1%E8%A8%88%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A.pdf |archive-date=2018-06-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

