==爭議==
{{see also2|{{le|2016年小丑目擊事件|2016 clown sightings}}}}
2016年10月，據報導，有人在[[南卡羅萊納州|南卡羅萊納州]][[格林維爾_(南卡羅萊納州)|格林維爾]]目擊到穿著邪惡小丑裝的人現身，當時一名9歲男孩告訴母親，兩名穿著小丑的可疑男子試圖將他引誘到附近的樹林中<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2016/oct/05/clown-sightings-south-carolina-alabama|title=Clown sightings: the day the craze began|last=Teague|first=Matthew|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=2016-10-08|accessdate=2016-10-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018155654/https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2016/oct/05/clown-sightings-south-carolina-alabama|archivedate=2016-10-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2016/oct/06/clown-sightings-stephen-king-it-pennywise|title=Stephen King tells US to 'cool the clown hysteria' after wave of sightings|last=Flood|first=Alison|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=2016-10-06|accessdate=2016-10-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161015043726/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2016/oct/06/clown-sightings-stephen-king-it-pennywise|archivedate=2016-10-15}}</ref>。在該事件發生後，有人認為是[[羅伯·殭屍|羅伯·殭屍]]電影《{{le|31 (電影)|31 (film)|31}}》的[[病毒式行銷|病毒式行銷]]一部分<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2016/09/07/clown-sightings-have-spread-to-north-carolina-now-police-are-concerned-about-creepy-copycats/|title=Clown sightings have spread to North Carolina. Now police are concerned about creepy copycats|last=Guarino|first=Ben|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=2016-09-07|accessdate=2016-10-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105060502/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2016/09/07/clown-sightings-have-spread-to-north-carolina-now-police-are-concerned-about-creepy-copycats/|archivedate=2016-11-05}}</ref>。格林維爾的警察局局長肯·米勒向記者表示，調查人員不確定這些目擊是否和《31》有關<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.greenvilleonline.com/story/news/local/2016/09/01/sheriffs-office-police-address-clown-sightings/89729508/|title=Police chief says clowns 'terrorizing public' will be arrested|last=Lee|first=Anna|work=The Greenville News|date=2016-09-01|accessdate=2016-10-22}}</ref>。有人懷疑這是否也和[[新線影業|新線影業]]的《牠》有關，但新線影業發聲明表示，該小丑目擊事件絕與新線無關<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/rambling-reporter/stephen-kings-movie-producer-denies-933077|title=Stephen King's 'It' Movie Producer Denies Creepy Clown Sightings Are Marketing Stunt|last=Gardner|first=Chris|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2016-09-29|accessdate=2016-10-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022171057/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/rambling-reporter/stephen-kings-movie-producer-denies-933077|archivedate=2016-10-22}}</ref>。

